name: UZ400
details:
Ultra FuzzKnockoff of the Boss FZ-3 Fuzz
Twist the dedicated Fuzz, Tone and Level dials to create a sound that's every bit as dirty as you want it to be. The blue LED tells you when it's activated and the on/off switch maintains outstanding signal integrity in bypass mode. You can power this box o' dirt with a 9 V battery or our PSU-SB DC power supply (not included).
